      • unmarshall

        public static SemanticRelationDescriptor unmarshall(String fileName)
        Load the SRD described in the XML file. If the file does not exists, an empty SRD is created.

        French:
        Charge le SRD decrit dans le fichier XML. Si le fichier n'existe pas, cree un nouveau SRD vide.

        Parameters:
        fileName - The name of the XML file describing the SRD to load.
        Returns:
        The SRD described in the XML file or an empty SRC if the XML file does not exist.

      • unmarshall

        public static SemanticRelationDescriptor unmarshall(String fileName,
                                                    Legend legend)
        Load the SRD described in the XML file using the component of the given Legend object. If the file does not exists, an empty SRD is created.

        French:
        Charge le SRD decrit dans le fichier XML en utilisant les composant de l'object Legend donné en paramètre. Si le fichier n'existe pas, cree un nouveau SRD vide.

        Parameters:
        fileName - The name of the XML file describing the SRD to load.
        legend - Legend
        Returns:
        The SRD described in the XML file or an empty SRC if the XML file does not exist.
